---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Series C Funding Gives Us the Chance to Work Smarter and Scale at Pace - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab announces $112 million Series C round to establish Operations Experience Management as a worldwide standard."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Series C Funding Gives Us the Chance to Work Smarter and Scale at Pace</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2021-06-14">June 14, 2021</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          These last few weeks have been a whirlwind, in the best possible way. We are thrilled to share the news of our Series C funding round. Just five years ago, the company consisted of just the two co-founders. Now, with 130 team members from over 20 countries, our success reflects collective effort.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Funding Announcement</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">$112 Million</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Series C round led by Insight Partners and Endeit Capital, alongside existing backers Capnamic Ventures and coparion.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Work Smarter</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Rather than rushing into new markets, we plan to strategically consider opportunities and bring in specialists for underdeveloped areas. The organization is actively hiring across departments with anticipated strong growth ahead.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          The focus shifts toward efficiency -- working intelligently rather than simply expanding faster. We intend to question previous approaches, maintaining our disruptor mentality while automating and reviewing existing processes to ensure true scaling, not just business growth.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">parcelLab + Operations Experience = The Future</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          We are grateful to our investors Insight Partners and Endeit Capital, alongside existing backers Capnamic Ventures and coparion. The $112 million Series C round reinforces confidence in our vision. We aim to establish Operations Experience Management as a worldwide standard that fundamentally reshapes how e-commerce brands approach strategy and operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          For our existing customers, the investment promises expanded product capabilities with new and refined features.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          From two co-founders to 130 team members across 20+ countries, the parcelLab journey continues. With this investment, we're positioned to work smarter, scale at pace, and establish Operations Experience Management as the global standard for ecommerce brands.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
